linear_regression.description: Tests association between SNP dosage and continuous phenotype

logistic_regression.description: Tests association between SNP dosage and binary phenotype
logistic_regression.output: beta, SE, z-statistic, p-value, odds ratio

gwas_best_practices_demonstrated: Use appropriate statistical model for phenotype type
Interpret effect sizes in biological context
Consider statistical power in study design
key_findings: Causal SNP 50 detected with strong association
Effect sizes range from small to large depending on SNP
Statistical power estimated at 99.0% for effect size 0.5

notes: Power depends on sample size, effect size, and variance
Larger effects are easier to detect
